# trysail

## Installation

```shell
pip install trysail
```

## Usage

```shell
trysail -h
```

## Example

```shell
# create a new radio project
trysail init -p radio
# enter project
cd radio-000001
trysail start
# write contents-001.txt, then parse
trysail parse
# prepare video at main-001.mp4, write main-001.ass, then finalize
trysail finalize
```

## Development

```shell
# install dev dependencies
pip install -r developer_requirements.txt

# local publish
cd publish
./publish_local.sh

# remote publish (first update version)
cd publish
./publish_remote.sh
```

